  <md:title>Lyndon Johnson and the Great Society</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list id="list-00001">
<item>Describe the major accomplishments of Lyndon Johnson’s Great Society</item>
<item>Identify the legal advances made in the area of civil rights</item>
<item>Explain how Lyndon Johnson deepened the American commitment in Vietnam</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>b4e291a3-6a27-49c1-9521-1cd06f416e99</md:uuid>
