   <definition id="fs-idm8800736">
<term>Great Society</term>
            <meaning id="fs-idp131815232">Lyndon Johnson’s plan to eliminate poverty and racial injustice in the United States and to improve the lives of all Americans</meaning>
</definition>
   <definition id="fs-idp223593440">
<term>war on poverty</term>
            <meaning id="fs-idm11837568">Lyndon Johnson’s plan to end poverty in the Unites States through the extension of federal benefits, job training programs, and funding for community development</meaning>
</definition>
